cat
# Interpreter for 'vpn-switch openvpn list' command
# Terminal function that outputs listing of configs and groups directly to user
#
# Default value: "cat"
#   Outputs directory listing directly to stdout (no execution needed)
#   Shows configuration files and group directories
#
# This is a terminal/display function - it should NOT execute commands.
# Use 'cat' to send output directly to the user without interpretation.
#
# Example output:
#   === OpenVPN Configurations ===
#   Configuration files:
#   us-server.ovpn
#   eu-server.ovpn
#   Groups:
#   work
#   personal
#
